Jiliaaa’s Book of Gold is an online slot game that takes players on an adventure through the pyramids of Egypt. The game is set in an ancient temple, with hieroglyphics covering the walls and pillars, and a golden book on the altar at the center of the room. The goal of the game is to uncover the secrets of the book and earn rewards in the process. Players spin the reels and hope to land matching symbols on the paylines. The book symbol serves as both the scatter and the wild, triggering free spins and substituting for other symbols. The game also features a gamble feature, allowing players to risk their winnings for a chance to double them. Jiliaaa’s Book of Gold offers an exciting and immersive gaming experience with the chance for big payouts. The game’s Egyptian theme and mystical elements make it a popular choice among players who enjoy adventure and mystery.

Book Of Gold Game Rules

Book Of Gold Slot Machine is a new Online Casino slot machine from JILI Gaming. Pack your bags and prepare to travel through history to explore one of the greatest tombs in ancient Egypt, seek divine guidance from the ancient Egyptian gods, and you will be able to find the greatest treasure through special symbols. Book of Gold slot machine comes with 5 x 3 reels. The maximum bonus multiplier is 1500X.

Book Of Gold Payline

  • Bet line wins pay if in succession starting from the leftmost reel to right according to paytable.
  • Special expansion symbols do not need to start from the left wheel and can appear continuously from left to right.
  • Only the biggest payout is considered for each payline .
  • Winnings =( Bet x Pay )/10.
  • In the event of any malfunction that causes the outcome of the game to be undecided, the game round will be invalid.

Book Of Gold Special Symbols

Wild

  • You can replace any in-game symbols except the Scatter Treasure Hunt symbol.
  • It always expand to the entire Roulette when it appears.

Scatter

  • It only appears on the 1st, 3rd, and 5th Roulette.
  • You can earn 3 Scatter Treasure Hunt symbol in normal games, which gives you 10 free rounds.
  • In a free game, for every 3 Scatter, you get 10 extra free rounds, up to 40.

Free Game

  • You need get three scatter symbol for start the free game, and you will get 10 free game for the round
  • Before a free game starts, you need to select the Special Expansion Symbol. (Except the WILD and Scatter Treasure Symbol.)
  • The Special Expansion Symbol will skip the bingo line and hit the jackpot, which then expand to the entire Roulette.

Extra Bets

  • Once the Extra Bets is enabled, you can select one more Special Expansion Symbol in the free game, making a total of two (except the WILD and Scatter Treasure Symbol).
  • Whenever there is a Wild, you always get 2.
